column2: SELECT  g.objID, g.ra,  g.dec, sp.plate,sp.mjd,sp.fiberid, sp.class, sp.subclass, g.fracDeV_g, g.fracDeV_r, g.modelmag_u,g.modelmagerr_u, g.modelmag_g,g.modelmagerr_g, g.modelmag_r,g.modelmagerr_r, g.modelmag_i,g.modelmagerr_i, g.modelmag_z,g.modelmagerr_z, g.cmodelmag_u,g.cmodelmagerr_u, g.cmodelmag_g,g.cmodelmagerr_g, g.cmodelmag_r,g.cmodelmagerr_r, g.cmodelmag_i,g.cmodelmagerr_i, g.cmodelmag_z,g.cmodelmagerr_z, g.dered_u, g.dered_g, g.dered_r, g.dered_i, g.dered_z, g.deVRad_g, g.deVRad_r, g.deVAB_g, dbo.fCosmoAbsMag(g.dered_r,sp.z,DEFAULT,DEFAULT,DEFAULT,DEFAULT,DEFAULT) as abs_mag_dered_r, g.specObjID, sp.z as redshift, sp.zErr as redshift_err, sp.z_noqso, sp.zErr_noqso, sp.veldisp as sp_vdisp, sp.veldisperr as sp_vdisp_err, pca.vdisp_median as pca_vdisp, pca.vdisp_err as pca_vdisp_err, pca.warning FROM Galaxy AS g JOIN specObjAll AS sp ON g.specObjID = sp.specObjID JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscBC0# AS pca ON g.specObjID = pca.specObjID WHERE (sp.mjd = #)
